Troubleshooting Tips
Tor Connection Issues:

Verify Tor service is running: sudo systemctl status tor
Check firewall settings allow port 9050
Test with curl --socks5 127.0.0.1:9050 https://check.torproject.org
Search Failures:

Increase timeout values in requests
Add longer delays between requests
Verify Ahmia.fi is accessible
Check proxy configuration in code
Parsing Errors:

Inspect HTML structure with browser developer tools
Update CSS selectors if Ahmia changes layout
Add try-except blocks around parsing code
Log raw HTML for debugging
